@The_Reaper_X wrote:

it’s probably best to not put your server ip up. Not only is it in the rules, but someone’s more likely to crash it now. Jut put contact information.

And you’re gonna need a better pitch than this, people see a lot of “best r00nsc4pe suv3r project EvR!” threads. Try to get it more professional, you might get more people interested ;]

As for me, I’m just here to help you out in this thread. I’m not as interested in your server, sorry. And good luck.
